<HEAD>29 Electrocuted in Bus Accident</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW DELHI, India (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Low-hanging power lines got entangled on
the roof of a bus, electrocuting 29 passengers, news reports said
Monday.
