<DATELINE>PARIS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   French undersea explorer Jacques Cousteau has
floated a whale over Paris to promote his new Museum of the Sea, due
to open July 11 in Paris' Les Halles district.
   The 30-meter dappled blue plastic mammal came up for air on
Sunday, bobbing in clear blue skies high above the traffic swirling
